29
00:01:40.780 --> 00:01:42.330
<font color="#00ffff">in der "Arena".</font>

30
00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:44.530
<font color="#00ffff">Wie soll man</font>
<font color="#00ffff">die Zuwanderung begrenzen</font>

31
