661
00:31:45.970 --> 00:31:47.830
<font color="#00ffff">Also noch einmal</font>
<font color="#00ffff">eine andere Variante.</font>

662
00:31:48.030 --> 00:31:49.630
<font color="#ffffff">* Signalton *</font>

